        </ul></li><li class="toplevel"><p><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/health-professional" class="level2">Health Professionals</a></p><ul><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/health-professional/cancer-statistics" class="level3">Cancer Statistics</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/cancer-info/cancerstats/local-cancer-statistics/" class="level3">Local cancer statistics</a></li><li><a href="http://www.cancerresearchuk.org/health-professional/early-diagnosis-activities/be-clear-on-cancer" class="level3">Be Clear on Cancer</a></li><li><a href="https://www.cancerresearchuk.org/health-professional/learning-and-development-tools/nice-cancer-referral-guidelines" class="level3">NICE suspected cancer referral guidelines</a></li>
        </ul></li></ul>
